system-tools-backends: system-tools-backends (freedesktop.org System Tools Backends)
system-tools-backends:
system-tools-backends: The System Tools Backends (s-t-b for short) are a set of cross-
system-tools-backends: platfor mmodules for Linux, FreeBSD and other Unix systems. The 
system-tools-backends: backends provide an common DBus interface to all platforms to modify 
system-tools-backends: or read the system configuration in a distro independent fashion.
system-tools-backends: System Tools Backends offers a generic and easy way for desktop 
system-tools-backends: applications to read and modify configuration details.
